Facial revitalisation acupuncture is a safe, painless, effective,
non surgical, non toxic process designed to help the whole body
both look and feel younger while reducing the signs of aging.
This treatment promotes a more youthful, glowing appearance by
encouraging natural collagen and elastin production, increased
circulation, and improved skin elasticity. FRA is firmly rooted in
the principles of oriental medicine, Like regular acupuncture, FRA
involves differential diagnosis and the use of multiple needles to
move or balance the qi, blood, and fluids within the body as well
as restore or maintain harmony. <br>
<br>

The observation of the face plays an important role in diagnosis
in Traditional Chinese Medicine (TCM)<a href="acupuntura#MTC">(TCM)</a>
because it is a reflection of a person's overall health. An important
sign of aging in the face is the appearance of wrinkles: the
attack of external pathogens, stress, anxiety and deficiency of
some organs can accelerate the aging process of the skin, favoring
its appearance. Negative emotions such as worry, stress, or anger
can also generate unconscious gestures - such as frowning - that
eventually develop into persistent wrinkles.

