As we age, all our bodily systems decline: our circulation slows down and can
become impeded, our hormonal levels drop, our ability to digest and absorb our
food decreases so that we no longer operate at our peak levels as we may have in
the past. FRA helps to bring all the bodily systems up to the optimum levels.
