<br>

Facial acupuncture is not only therapeutic (for people who already have signs of
aging in the face) but also acts preventively so it is recommended for people who
are beginning to show signs of aging on the face etc. It works for anyone from 25
years of age because from that age the skin begins to lose its essential proteins,
including collagen and elastin. The condition of the skin not only
depends on the individual and his or her age but on several other factors - genetics,
damages, sun dammage, synthetic facial products, stress levels, anxiety and
lifestyle.<br>

